textAfterTable: 14 Songs Biography Formed: 1998 in Minneapolis, MN Genre: Hip-Hop/Rap Years Active: '90s, '00s, '10s Atmosphere are a hip-hop group from Minneapolis centering around rapper Slug (aka Sean Daley). The son of a black father and a white mother who divorced when he was a teenager, Slug became entranced with hip-hop, graffiti, and breakdancing, and formed the Rhymesayers collective with two high-school friends — Siddiq Ali (Stress) and Derek Turner (Spawn).
